These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
City: miami, marseilles
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, techno
1. the fan of trance is not to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##8
2. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| City          | marseilles | miami    |
| Flower         | iris   | zinnia |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | techno      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: cherry, nectarine
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, june
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, disaster
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
4. the person watching family movies is not the person eating nectarine##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Food       | cherry         | nectarine |
| Birthday         | june | april   |
| Movie-Genre   | family               | disaster  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, old-henry
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, purple
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the person who likes purple##8
3. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall       | old-henry |
| Transport   | bike       | jet-ski    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Color           | lavender        | purple   |

