.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, sudoku
2 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog
City: marseilles, rome
There 2 different types of food: pear, cranberry
1. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | frog |
| City   | rome | marseilles   |
| Food     | cranberry   | pear |

