.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, soul
House: cape-cod, cottage
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, july
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the fan of punk is not to the left of the cottage house##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the fan of soul##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Music-Genre        | punk | soul            |
| House       | cottage | cape-cod              |
| Birthday         | october  | july |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

